Our restaurant  was the first Japanese restaurant in Oregon, which makes us the initiators of an exceptional culinary story in the region and beyond.We have spent 25 successful years at our first location in Astoria. In the spring of 2016, to the delight of many fans of the Japanese, but also exotic food, we took our business to a higher level. The eclectic feel of the location in Astoria was transferred to the heart of Oregon, on the corner of 5th and 29th in a brand new area  and a capacity of 80-odd seats. 

 The business tradition and the continued high level of artistry resulted in winning numerous awards.
